<A>__{peaceful day by pennywise blasts on danny’s walkman headphones. the day is cloudy and overcast but that doesn’t bother the local surfers. a twosome paddles north to get a better break on the next set. danny watches as he skateboards aggressively down the strand. his appearance is changed, now resembling a young version of derek. he stops for a moment, scratches his head with his cigarette laden hand, and takes a deep drag. head shaved to a quarter of an inch, he wears a plain white backpack with punk bands scribbled all over it. your standard sex pistols, dk, the germs, g.b.h., and adolescence in black. outlined in red is the largest name, dick nixon.}
